title: PPPP wins NA-223 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan People’s Party Parliamentarian Candidate Syed Javed Ali Shah Jilani has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-204 Khairpur-III by securing 1,12,249 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Grand Democratic Alliance candidate Moazzam Ali Khan, who bagged 87,501 votes.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 43.52 percent.
